* '''Player:''' I think I know how to carry out the task.
* '''Felkrash:''' Has the face{{sic}} being{{sic}} telling tall tales again?
* '''Player:''' Oh no, she didn't say a word.
* '''Player:''' Really she didn't.
* {{tact|end}}

